VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT resource\s+"aws_s3_bucket"\s*"[^"]+"\s*\{
WHEN EXPR MISSING:server_side_encryption_configuration|aws_s3_bucket_server_side_encryption_configuration
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects S3 buckets or storage resources without server-side encryption configured.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Storage Encryption Disabled or Not Configured.
